{"tid":1202037,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"一流的公民，下流的政府 - 高慧然","createTime":"2019-06-11T07:43:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T07:55:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e3ff61d60d96fac48839a5bf749608a019cdf386","tid":1202037,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:43:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20190611/20700485\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190611%2F20700485&d=%2Bbf%2BkhF7pVXIIu5z8NbAo870t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=4ad27b9e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190611%2F20700485&h=42d05871\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20190611/20700485</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一流的公民，下流的政府 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190611/large/e8810a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190611%2Flarge%2Fe8810a.jpg&h=93375dbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n歷史會記住這一天，2019年6月9日，103萬香港人走上街頭，向獨裁治港政府推出的《逃犯條例》修訂說不。同一日，居住在全球29個城巿的香港人發動遊行或集會，聲援香港人。澳洲Perth則提前一日，在6月8日舉行遊行，由巿中心Yagan Square遊行至中國領事館。我的Calgary朋友發給我相片及短片，告訴我，本來只是集會，因為群情激昂，結果改作遊行，由中國領事館遊行至唐人街。遊行隊伍沿途用廣東話高喊「反送中」、「林鄭下台」。<br />\n<br />\n看到103萬港人遊行的相片，看到移居外國但仍然熱愛自己家鄉的香港人，我無法抑制淚水狂奔，是感動，更多的，卻是憤怒。回想九七之後，香港人一次又一次上街，遊行了多少次？香港人是如此優秀的人，跟全世界所有民主國家的選民相比，香港人毫不遜色！香港人有良好的公民質素，熱愛自由、民主、法治，用一己之力去守護自己的地方，這樣一流的公民，為甚麼要遭受如此苦難，被剝奪本身擁有的權利，由民主社會陷入獨裁專制手中？香港人做錯了甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n林鄭說過當主流民意不滿，她會辭職，言猶在耳，面對100多萬香港人的怒吼，她卻選擇了無視。一個公務員，在全世界眾目睽睽之下，安然做她的獨裁者。這麼無恥的人，帶領一個下流的管治隊伍，有甚麼資格管治香港？  <br />\n<br />\n高慧然 <br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n他們不配管治香港 (曾志豪)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n一青二白和一團漿糊 (李純恩)"},{"pid":"4350ae57f8b6ac0efdfc78f78a673a0c747e7893","tid":1202037,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:46:41.000Z","msg":"係有心返黎幫拖啦 係外國行做乜鳩"},{"pid":"3591f96bb5ddc40bd2f9470ecf7953749fc3561f","tid":1202037,"uid":187905,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4350ae57f8b6ac0efdfc78f78a673a0c747e7893","tid":1202037,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:46:41.000Z","msg":"係有心返黎幫拖啦 係外國行做乜鳩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:49:15.000Z","msg":"好過唔幫，人左外國唔係個個放得低而家手頭上嘅嘢"},{"pid":"906b617fd6f57fa38db47ea2846e34286dc41e27","tid":1202037,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4350ae57f8b6ac0efdfc78f78a673a0c747e7893","tid":1202037,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:46:41.000Z","msg":"係有心返黎幫拖啦 係外國行做乜鳩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:49:19.000Z","msg":"同97移民海外跟住聲援香港嘅一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb035739b7108b3afc985f0ec636a9f9708364c","tid":1202037,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3591f96bb5ddc40bd2f9470ecf7953749fc3561f","tid":1202037,"uid":187905,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4350ae57f8b6ac0efdfc78f78a673a0c747e7893","tid":1202037,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:46:41.000Z","msg":"係有心返黎幫拖啦 係外國行做乜鳩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:49:15.000Z","msg":"好過唔幫，人左外國唔係個個放得低而家手頭上嘅嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:52:29.000Z","msg":"On9 咁唔好當自己係香港人"},{"pid":"013f78060d48d3aff3f71f69618312048e20e310","tid":1202037,"uid":215249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T07:52:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BVIONKoS3Yg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBVIONKoS3Yg&d=%